<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>CLAUDE.md</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>file<sp/>provides<sp/>guidance<sp/>to<sp/>Claude<sp/>Code<sp/>(claude.ai/code)<sp/>when<sp/>working<sp/>with<sp/>code<sp/>in<sp/>this<sp/>repository.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Project<sp/>Overview</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Aperture<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>security-focused<sp/>programming<sp/>language<sp/>that<sp/>uses<sp/>&quot;apertures&quot;<sp/>(holes)<sp/>to<sp/>enable<sp/>secure<sp/>distributed<sp/>computation.<sp/>The<sp/>secure<sp/>implementation<sp/>allows<sp/>untrusted<sp/>servers<sp/>to<sp/>optimize<sp/>and<sp/>partially<sp/>evaluate<sp/>computations<sp/>without<sp/>accessing<sp/>sensitive<sp/>data.<sp/>Expressions<sp/>with<sp/>holes<sp/>(marked<sp/>with<sp/>`?variable`)<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>partially<sp/>evaluated,<sp/>preserving<sp/>privacy<sp/>while<sp/>enabling<sp/>optimization.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Build<sp/>Commands</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```bash</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Compile<sp/>secure<sp/>language<sp/>implementation<sp/>(C++23<sp/>required)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>demo.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>demo</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Compile<sp/>and<sp/>run<sp/>tests</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>unit_tests.cpp<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>unit_tests</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>integration_tests.cpp<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>integration_tests</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Compile<sp/>fluent<sp/>API<sp/>demos</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>fluent_demo.cpp<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>fluent_demo</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>simple_fluent_demo.cpp<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>simple_fluent_demo</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Compile<sp/>secure<sp/>computation<sp/>demo</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-std=c++23<sp/>-O2<sp/>secure_computation_demo.cpp<sp/>secure_lang.cpp<sp/>-o<sp/>secure_demo</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Run<sp/>Python<sp/>validation<sp/>tests</highlight></codeline>
